            <description>&lt;p&gt;
	Alfa Laval India Limited is a Swedish company and is the market in more than 50 countries across globe. They have a mature Lean Manufacturing System.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;br /&gt;&lt;img src="http://feeds.feedburner.com/~r/noria/reliableplant/tags/5-S/~4/yaU57xLwcK8" height="1" width="1" alt=""/&gt;</description>
