            <guid isPermaLink="false">tag:noria.com,2010-06-10:publishing:magazines:rp:4a8437b3-874b-4a42-9d0d-9cf800da18de</guid>
            <link>http://feedproxy.google.com/~r/noria/reliableplant/tags/5-S/~3/x9ZmHWqgBoI/5s-program</link>
